subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kia Vaughn was 12 of 16 from the field and finished with a career-high 27 points to lead No. 19 Rutgers to a 76-51 victory against Princeton on Saturday night.
